@MadalynSklar 1|2 Social listening on Twitter is as easy as searching for keywords in the search bar. The real issue is knowing WHAT to listen for.

What are people saying about your brand? What's happening at an event? What're your competitors up to?

You can listen for that. #TwitterSmarter https://twitter.com/hootsuite/status/1359928398009815040/photo/1

@Tricycle_Europe Love to hear it. And we're sure your friends and family will  benefit from your new cooking skills too!

PS you've got an awesome name 👍

- Also Nick

@MadalynSklar 2|2 Our second tip is to keep your keyword search brief: 1 - 3 word searches will do the trick. Get creative and find a fun one to share. 

We dare you to search @GIPHY's GIF library for "hootsuite" 😏

In the end, GIFs are meant to be fun. So have fun with them! #TwitterSmarter https://twitter.com/hootsuite/status/1403037513619476487/photo/1

